snippet.title: Accel Knights 2: Full Throttle Gameplay Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Accel Knights 2: Full Throttle Walkthrough

Let's Play - Accel Knights 2: Full Throttle

ABOUT THIS GAME

A boy fights against his destiny and becomes a knight!

This work is the second battle action story game following "Accel Knights ~Take the sword for you~" (Nintendo DSiWare) released in 2010. You can enjoy even more exhilarating and deep battles by improving the battle system.

The character designer is Shintaro Mashima. As for the sound, Basiscape heats up the dramatic world.
